headline.main: Dr. Janet Anderson Caldwell, 82, Pathologist and Nutrition Expert

docs.lead_paragraph: Dr. Janet Anderson Caldwell, a pathologist and an expert in nutrition, died Monday at her Manhattan home. She was 82 years old.
